{"sections":{"main":{"type":"article-template","custom_css":[".article .section-header__title {text-transform: none;}"],"settings":{"image_hero":false,"blog_show_tags":true,"blog_show_date":false,"blog_show_comments":false,"blog_show_author":false,"social_sharing_blog":false}},"text_and_image_ebhjYT":{"type":"text-and-image","settings":{"custom_id":"","full_width":false,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/rsz_mdm_ago20_0348.jpg","image_mask":"none","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"","caption":"","title":"","text":"<p>Jewelry is one of the most timeless gifts, symbolizing love, style, and luxury. At MARCO DAL MASO, each piece is crafted to turn every moment into a lasting memory, whether you’re celebrating a milestone or adding a special touch to daily wear. <\/p><p><\/p><p>Discover options for men and women that make unforgettable gifts.<\/p>","html":"","button_label":"","button_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/ulysses-slick-ring-oxidized-silver-black-diamond-black-enamel-agan0047-01bven","button_labels":"","button_links":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"50","layout":"right","body_bg":"#ffffff","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true,"lazyload_images":true}},"rich_text_X4YKkz":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_reYjpA":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<h3><strong>Why Jewelry Makes the Perfect Gift<\/strong><\/h3><p><\/p><p>Jewelry is a meaningful gift that tells a story. <\/p><p>With MARCO DAL MASO, every piece reflects quality craftsmanship and thoughtful design, making it the perfect way to mark significant occasions. <\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_reYjpA"],"settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"left","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"text_with_products_EQLiJY":{"type":"text-with-products","blocks":{"image_mkiet4":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AGCL146-01BV47_1__G_9dad0a76-f2a6-4244-816d-689946ef7118.png","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/ulysses-faceted-marine-chain-necklace-47cm-agcl146-01bv47"}},"image_wh8THV":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AGAN0053-01BV_1__G_d7343a02-ed60-4698-a442-2a9f5f858b9e.png","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/ulysses-carved-chain-ring-oxidized-silver-agan0053-01bv"}}},"block_order":["image_mkiet4","image_wh8THV"],"settings":{"custom_id":"","full_width":true,"subtitle":"","title":"","text":"<h3><strong>Men’s Jewelry Gift Ideas<\/strong><\/h3><p><\/p><p>For men, silver chains or minimalist rings are versatile staples, ideal for everyday wear or special occasions.<\/p><p><\/p><p>If he prefers bolder looks, our signet rings and thicker chains add a powerful touch to any outfit. <\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"50","layout":"left","body_bg":"#ffffff","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true,"lazyload_images":true}},"text_and_image_JfTUUA":{"type":"text-and-image","settings":{"custom_id":"","full_width":false,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/rsz_dsc04424.jpg","image_mask":"none","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"","caption":"","title":"","text":"<p>Pieces like engraved bracelets make unique birthday or holiday gifts, while <a href=\"https:\/\/marcodalmaso.com\/en-it\/products\/flaming-tongue-18k-yellow-gold-black-diamond-id-bracelet\" target=\"_blank\">diamond-studded designs<\/a> are perfect for commemorating anniversaries or other milestones.<\/p><p><\/p><p>For the graduate, MARCO DAL MASO’s <a href=\"https:\/\/marcodalmaso.com\/collections\/triumph\" target=\"_blank\">Triumph collection<\/a> offers a way to celebrate this important milestone with a gift of style and sophistication.<\/p>","html":"","button_label":"","button_link":"\/products\/ulysses-slick-oxidized-ring-with-black-diamond-black-enamel?_pos=4&_sid=82799d952&_ss=r","button_labels":"","button_links":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"50","layout":"right","body_b